"    Stimate <span style=\"font-weight:bold;\" t-"
"out=\"object.partner_id.display_name or ''\"/>,<br/>\n"
"    <br/> \n"
"    Comanda dumneavoastră <span style=\"font-weight:bold;\" t-"
